"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"US Defence Secretary Pete Hegseth says Iran is trying to pressure other countries in the strait. Iran warned the US that they are just beginning.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran Pressure\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Secretario de Defensa de EE.UU., Pete Hegseth, dice que Ir\u00e1n est\u00e1 tratando de presionar a otros pa\u00edses en el estrecho. Ir\u00e1n advirti\u00f3 a EE.UU. que solo est\u00e1n comenzando.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presi\u00f3n de Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A blast at a fireworks factory in Hunan province killed 26 people and injured 61, according to state media.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fireworks Factory Blast\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una explosi\u00f3n en una f\u00e1brica de fuegos artificiales en la provincia de Hunan mat\u00f3 a 26 personas y hiri\u00f3 a 61, seg\u00fan los medios estatales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Explosi\u00f3n en F\u00e1brica\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kyiv announced it would start a truce on 6 May and then respond in kind after Moscow declared a pause for its Victory Day parade.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kyiv Truce\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kyiv anunci\u00f3 que comenzar\u00eda una tregua el 6 de mayo y luego responder\u00eda igual despu\u00e9s de que Mosc\u00fa declarara una pausa para su desfile del D\u00eda de la Victoria.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tregua de Kyiv\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A 33-year-old German citizen was detained after an incident, according to authorities.\",            \"english_title\": \"German Citizen Detained\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ciudadano alem\u00e1n de 33 a\u00f1os fue detenido despu\u00e9s de un incidente, seg\u00fan las autoridades.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Detenido Alem\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Film star Vijay has surprised critics by almost winning the Tamil Nadu elections, changing the political scene.\",            \"english_title\": \"Vijay's Political Surprise\",            \"translated_version\": \"La estrella de cine Vijay ha sorprendido a los cr\u00edticos al casi ganar las elecciones de Tamil Nadu, cambiando la escena pol\u00edtica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Sorpresa Pol\u00edtica de Vijay\"        }    ]}"